{"tid":1682071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港黃色經濟法案","createTime":"2019-10-29T23:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T06:32:33.000Z","uid":50457,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03118b1f1dc0f88b94afeff86f3694753e070db3","tid":1682071,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T23:54:15.000Z","msg":"真黃色店舖可以經得起考驗，而假黃色店舖一遇小事就會露餡<br />\n<br />\n紅色資本，永久柸葛<br />\n<br />\n藍色資本，每年重估<br />\n<br />\n黃色資本，大力支持<br />\n<br />\n透過經濟制裁紅色資本，限制中共，港共爪牙的氣焰。永久制裁，就會有永久的對抗力。"},{"pid":"d3b6d61e5c259f60b78c82a6212b5b74df5da3e0","tid":1682071,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T23:54:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人(眾籌到而家先30%, 仲要大家支持) <br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=68b32e79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"97c40a76c79151a2b196a240afc0f619a4b806e7","tid":1682071,"uid":234944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"借個位，利用網上廣告懲罰紅色資本<br />\n<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/y5b32rzj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fy5b32rzj&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=4571f0e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/y5b32rzj</a>"},{"pid":"2dff3bba7f97f7d93c8eaceb8321160639fcaca1","tid":1682071,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T05:50:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"431c384ccc8643c8b064365418c254d5fa5a0c93","tid":1682071,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":